Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:01:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have finally arrived at the location of the Final, Alcatraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we're going to settle Battle City on this Duel Tower built atop a pile of scrap?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and myself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The four finalists have gathered and are now fighting against one another in a Battle Royale!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How should I fight in this battle meant to decide our opponents in the Semi-Finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle Royale!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Yugi!\N You're backing {\i1}Jounouchi{\i0} up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you one, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me to play Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} in the Semi-Finals,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to make sure Kaiba and Malik's Life Points hit zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, in order to ensure that happens, I won't let you attack Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s Life Points any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, my life has been dictated by one purpose... and that purpose is to {\b0}defeat you{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And to win this battle is my {\b0}fate{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And above all, I must use the Obelisk I hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and use it to win the Osiris {\b0}you{\b1} possess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need two so I stand a chance against the God Card {\b0}he{\b1} owns, the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, in order for me to dominate Battle City...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as well as to earn the title of "Duel King"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:03:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I {\b0}will{\b1} face you in the Semi-Finals, even if I have to drag you there myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks a lot, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He wants to face me in the Semi-Finals so he can keep our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, I really wanna fight against you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't beat that guy, Mai may never wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai's been waiting a long time now for me to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scrub like you {\i1}needs {\i0}Yugi's protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose a deadbeat like yourself can't manage to be a Duelist on his {\i1}own{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I dare you to say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you two friendship-obsessing dweebs want to keep your promise to Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just think about it, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Yugi help somebody like {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the Semi-Finals is your only chance to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, regardless of who you face in the Semi-Finals, your chances of getting into the Final are 0%!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of your general lack of skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact remains that the three of us have {\i1}God Cards{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi {\i1}knows{\i0} that the Semi-Finals will be your only chance to face him in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yugi {\i1}also{\i0} knows that he'll be able to easily wipe the floor with you as a warm-up for the {\i1}real{\i0} challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you would try such underhanded tactics right in the middle of the Battle City Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really insult me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! I won't let you insult him any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Insult{\i0} him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to prove my words wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't you leave your friendship nonsense out the window and settle things with me fair and square in the proper battlefield?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful that you saved me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is my fight and my fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rattled by Kaiba's crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you in the Final, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your words cast my doubt away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just the howling of a loser dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for you, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll be fighting {\b0}me{\b1} in the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay strong, Mai-{\i0}san{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! That's dangerous, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, but we're in a hurry here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get moving, Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you guys know Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This girl is Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're being chased by some weird people called "Ghouls".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ghouls...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have decided that the first thing I want to see when my eyes are healed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is the sight of my big brother fighting his hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never knew Jounouchi\N had such a cute sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure he'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really is a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's kind... and courageous...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even back in Duelist Kingdom, he fought for you as if his very life was at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I'm certain the brother you see will be one who will never betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai-{\i0}san{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I may have over-exaggerated a bit there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's fighting his hardest right now, believing that you're going to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And cheer my brother on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Tournament Final has finally begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. Last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0}Rishid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0}Save Rishid from that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I followed Malik's pleading and moved Rishid to another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I haven't heard\N Malik's voice since then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has Malik's soul disappeared altogether?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or has he been completely trapped by his dark half's Power of Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This tragedy started\N when you collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the very day after...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik disappeared along with Rishid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And they took the Millennium Rod with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that tragedy, my tribe's mission failed miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It faded away into the World of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Millennium Tauk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you trying to tell me that this is only the beginning of the tragedy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soon after, Malik stole the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra and Osiris the Heaven Dragon cards from the Valley of the Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will not find the Obelisk the War God card here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been some time, big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This can't just be coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For us to meet here this way, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik! Ghouls! Turn yourselves in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give it up, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I take it you're now the official in charge of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, it does make sense that a member of the Tomb Guardians would want to protect the palette depicting the God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik! Return the Ra and Osiris cards this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They belong to {\b0}me{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as this Millennium Rod does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! They belong to the nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They must be returned\N to their rightful owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you forgotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our tragedy... no, the tragedy of the Tomb Guardians...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of it happened {\b0}because{\b1} of the nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to find him no matter what it takes, and take {\b0}revenge{\b1} on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop this at once, Malik!\N Your fate has already been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:11:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're only going to cause {\b0}another{\b1} tragedy to occur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scars carved into my back...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scars Rishid implanted in his face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you trying to tell me that our suffering was not caused by the nameless Pharaoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will never accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big sister... Using the Millennium Rod, I have organized the Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using this power, I will be able to kill the nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once I {\b0}become{\b1} the Pharaoh, I will change the fate of the Tomb Guardians forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And when that moment comes, my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will come back to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the three of us shall live together like we used to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, you will not get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big sister, I {\b0}will{\b1} get my hands on the remaining Obelisk card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the only one who can stop the other Malik from awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to prevent it, you have chosen to walk the same path as Malik, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid... Now that you have fallen once more, all that's left of Malik's soul is his evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thinking back on it now, everything has been chosen by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A young boy named Yugi solving the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus discovering the location of the palette...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and creating Duel Monsters as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto Kaiba obtaining the God Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ours... as well as Malik's future...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They all ride on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue the Duel already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it be your sealed memory or the Tomb Guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You piss me off in\N more ways than I can count!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So my target in the Semi-Finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's {\b0}you{\b1}, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But first I'll sweep away all of these other yapping fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I Summon Lord Poison!\N Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Newdoria goes into Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brace yourself, Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to reserve my fight with Yugi, I have to eliminate {\b0}you{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdoria attacks Kaiba's Blood Vorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! Attacking me with a Monster that has lower Attack Power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does Malik's Monster have some kind of Special Ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Vorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdoria dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Special Ability activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment he is placed in the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his curse destroys one Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Vorse!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:15:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes! Now Kaiba's field is wide open! The bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take 700 points of damage this turn because of that attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will now activate this Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spell of Pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a card that transfers damage you receive to one of the other players!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who will\N take this effect... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall activate this effect on Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, your gondola rises 700 units thanks to the points you lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...! I'm closest to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! You only lost 700 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine! There's still a chance to turn things around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for {\i1}you{\i0} to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got no Monsters on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm totally at a disadvantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as planned, Kaiba's Monster was destroyed and the damage was sent to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And on my next turn, I'll sacrifice this Monster to Summon a better Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, Kaiba doesn't have any Monsters on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take him out with one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Summon the Archfiend of Gilfer Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bring it on, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilfer Flame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was naive, Yugi!\N I read right through that strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Guidance Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card redirects any attack sent my way to the Monster attached to this armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A card that switches the attack target...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}could{\i0} make your Gilfer Demon attack himself, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then... Who do I pick...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait, I don't even {\i1}have{\i0} a Monster in play...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place the Guidance Armor on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...{\i1}your{\i0} Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to take Gilfer Demon's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Force?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now your Gilfer Demon's attack will be negated, Yugi, and all of your Monsters will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Tools of the Bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card negates the activation of your Mirror Force and destroys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0} did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really heating up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik! You just lost some of your Life in the attack just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, your gondola will rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik's Life Points are the same as mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. I hope you don't think you can simply forget about this, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost of using that Seven Tools of the Bandit you just played is 1000 of your Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}you'll{\i0} be rising along with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}well{\i0} aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's the closest to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! The point in this Battle Royale {\i1}isn't{\i0} to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still choose the opponent you want even if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you to hell, Yugi...! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you {\b0}still{\b1} trying to fight with that deadbeat in the Semi-Finals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have a Monster Card in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Iron Knight Gearfried!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally got a Monster out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, who should I attack...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba and Malik both used their face-down cards on Yugi's turn just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And they don't have any Monsters to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which one should I attack though?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an easy pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Direct Attack {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba has no way to defend himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Kaiba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...! How {\i1}dare{\i0} a lowly scrub like {\i1}you{\i0} wound {\i1}me{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaiba! I'm gonna send you to the top just like you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a {\i1}loser{\i0}, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now Malik and Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} are closest together in the gondolas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} went after Kaiba instead of attacking Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could that mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does that mean he wants to fight Malik himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai's life could end at any time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}have{\b1} to beat Malik in the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also place a card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that if I attack Yugi and find a way to off myself in the process...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would be guaranteed to fight Yugi in the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for me to {\b0}lose{\b1} before the Semi-Finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I set three reverse cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, I then Summon Blade Knight in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Knocking that deadbeat out can wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be attacking {\i1}you{\i0}, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn...! Now it's gotten harder for me to fight Malik in the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Malik is closer to the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wonder who will end up fighting who.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no room for {\i1}failure{\i0} on my road of battle...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I need to do is dispose of Malik and the deadbeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and defeat Yugi in the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you {\i0}also{\i1} want to show them all, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our battle of the gods!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the four continue to face off in the Battle Royale,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Duel is getting so complex that we can't tell the ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi finds himself in trouble when he gets attacked by both Kaiba and Mallik at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as Yugi is about to attack, Jounouchi suddenly asks him a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"What does it mean to be a True Duelist"...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Respective Opponents"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:23:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
